Definition: doctrine that the useful is the good
Example: especially as elaborated by Jeremy Bentham and James Mill; the aim was said to be the greatest happiness for the greatest number
Synonyms: doctrine, that, the, useful, is, good, especially, as, elaborated, by, Jeremy, Bentham, and, James, Mill, aim, was, said, to, be, greatest, happiness, for, number
Category: noun.cognition
